    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Leave of Absence Taken at Fitzgerald</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Stuart Elliot</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Jim Paddock will take one-year leave of absence as executive vice president and chief creative officer at Fitzgerald &amp; Company; Mark Gettner will assume his duties (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Jim Paddock, executive vice president and chief creative officer at Fitzgerald &amp; Company in Atlanta, part of the Interpublic Group of Companies, is taking a one-year leave of absence, the agency said yesterday.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Jim Paddock, executive vice president and chief creative officer at Fitzgerald &amp; Company in Atlanta, part of the Interpublic Group of Companies, is taking a one-year leave of absence, the agency said yesterday.</p>
        <p>Mr. Paddock, 53, will leave at the end of the year. Mark Gettner, 36, vice president and group creative director, was named senior vice president and executive creative director, assuming the duties Mr. Paddock has handled.</p>
        <p>THE MEDIA BUSINESS: ADVERTISING -- ADDENDA</p>
      </block>
